Package it.polimi.wifidirect.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClientList
    Class that represents the list of device connect to the group owner.
    LocalP2PDevice
    Class that represents the P2PDevice associated to this device.
    P2PDevice
    Class that represents a P2PDevice with inside a android.net.wifi.p2p.WifiP2pDevice and the groupOwner attribute.
    P2PGroup
    Class that represents a P2PGroup with inside a android.net.wifi.p2p.WifiP2pDevice and other parameters like, P2PGroup.persistent, the go's P2PDevice, the go's ip address, and the entire list of clients, if this device is a GO.
    P2PGroups
    Class that contain a list of the groups of this device.
    PeerList
    Class that represents the list of device discovered during the discovery phase.
    PingPongList
    Class that represents the list of GO's mac address available to pingpong with the PingPong device client.
